WEBVTT

00:07.901 --> 00:14.603
Even among Sahaja Yogis, I am very
sorry to say, there are some racists.

00:15.764 --> 00:20.701
Because Grégoire said just now
I am sorry to say that so many girls

00:20.781 --> 00:24.054
who are married in the West are extremely unhappy.

00:24.134 --> 00:29.165
And already I’ve received a notice
from Sahaja Yogis from India

00:29.245 --> 00:34.253
that they don’t want to marry any Indian girls to Westerners.

00:34.346 --> 00:38.725
I know of Sahaja Yogis who ill-treat their wives,

00:39.865 --> 00:47.338
in England, in Switzerland and in many places like that.

00:47.418 --> 00:53.539
To overcome this all such yogis should
beat themselves with shoes themselves

00:53.619 --> 00:57.549
or ask their wives to beat them, that’s what they deserve.

00:57.629 --> 01:00.462
It is a very dangerous sign because they will get immobilized

01:00.542 --> 01:03.336
and Sahaja Yoga will get a bad name.

01:03.416 --> 01:06.781
It is so imminent and I am so much worried

01:06.861 --> 01:10.633
that I would say that Sahaja yogis if they come to know such a man

01:10.713 --> 01:16.261
they should get hold of him and give him
fifty one shoes nicely on his head.

01:17.215 --> 01:23.254
And all such racists must know that
if they had married anybody from their own country

01:23.334 --> 01:27.511
they would have had nice slaps on their face every day.

01:27.591 --> 01:33.238
All this is very saddening some times even on this day

01:33.319 --> 01:37.195
when I am sitting before you, I have come to know of stories

01:37.275 --> 01:41.120
that I am shocked the way people behaved.

01:41.527 --> 01:47.730
You have to know that India is a blissful country.
That’s why we go there.

01:47.810 --> 01:52.990
From that blissful country to come
these horrid countries it is not easy.

01:53.070 --> 01:55.298
I know how difficult it is.

01:55.571 --> 02:00.568
I have called all this Sahaja Yoginis
that you go and learn something from them.

02:00.648 --> 02:03.235
Instead of that, you start criticizing them.

02:03.315 --> 02:05.541
It’s better that you have no more of them here.

02:05.622 --> 02:09.492
This is the reason I brought them here
because you don’t know anything.

02:09.632 --> 02:13.329
They know so many things about your country.

02:13.562 --> 02:18.258
They have learnt your science, so many things,

02:18.958 --> 02:24.381
why can’t you become a proper Sahaja Yogi
to know that they know

02:24.461 --> 02:27.669
more than knowledge of the roots?

02:27.749 --> 02:33.204
And that will give Me greatest joy

02:33.284 --> 02:38.456
when I will see there is not a
single racist left in Sahaja Yoga.

02:38.869 --> 02:42.517
If in Sahaja Yoga somebody gets immobilized,

02:42.661 --> 02:46.643
please don’t blame Me because
I have warned you on such a day

02:46.723 --> 02:50.634
when you all are here and I did not want
to say all this things today

02:50.714 --> 02:52.714
but there is no other way out.
